    public static class GuiConfigEntries.SelectValueEntry
extends GuiConfigEntries.ButtonEntry
    SelectValueEntry Provides a GuiButton with the current value as the displayString. Accepts a Map of selectable values with the signature where the key is the Object to be selected and the value is the String that will show on the selection list. EG: a map of Mod ID values where the key is the Mod ID and the value is the Mod Name.
